Install development dependencies:
```bash
uv sync --dev
```

Run tests:
```bash
RBT_ROOT_DIR=/test/root uv run pytest -v
```

Test coverage:
```bash
RBT_ROOT_DIR=/test/root uv run pytest --cov=rbt_mcp_server --cov-report=html
```

